snippet.title: Official 3089 Trailer (v9)
snippet.description:
3089 is a futuristic action role-playing game featuring random terrain, weapons, enemies, items, quests & more. Now available on Steam!

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/263360/

Play the free demo @ http://3089game.wordpress.com/

You are a promising robotic android design, made by the Overlord, placed on planet Xax.

Your performance in common combat, support & intel scenarios is being closely watched. However, will you become too much for them to handle? What else on planet Xax exists that the Overlord doesn't know about?

Logo Art by burningpet
Engine: jMonkeyEngine 3
Music by https://soundcloud.com/fawstoar
Video taken from v1.1.3 gameplay
